In this database contains of civil department students information

Created and Inserted the 2 tables:
  1. Student basic info(name,student_id,course,branch,mobile) inserted all values✅
  2. Time table (day,subject,roo_no,time {start,end},period)  inserted all values✅
DESCRIPTION:
Sno	int	NO	PRI		auto_increment
name	varchar(50)	YES			
student_id	varchar(10)	YES	UNI		
course	varchar(15)	YES			
branch	varchar(10)	YES			
section	varchar(1)	YES			
place	varchar(25)	YES			
mobile	bigint	YES


Updation method i use here:
Room Updation:

UPDATE timetablec2
SET room_no = CASE
WHEN day = '--Day--' AND period = 1 THEN '--room_no--'
WHEN day = '--Day--' AND period = 2 THEN '--room_no--'
WHEN day = '--Day--' AND period = 3 THEN '--room_no--'
WHEN day = '--Day--' AND period = 4 THEN '--room_no--'
WHEN day = '--Day--' AND period = 5 THEN '--room_no--'
WHEN day = '--Day--' AND period = 6 THEN '--room_no--'
WHEN day = '--Day--' AND period = 7 THEN '--room_no--'
WHEN day = '--Day--' AND period = 8 THEN '--room_no--'
ElSE room_no
END
WHERE day = '--Day--' AND Sno >1;

According to that i used sam method for subjects and other.

